6370238202365331036.Text: I gave Han-Ammu the Sanit-Kil's Heart of Fire and made a little speech about courage and symbols and responsibility. I believe he has taken the lesson to heart, and will consider accepting his responsibilities as ashkhan, and consider naming me Nerevarine. But he said he didn't need the amulet, and he let me keep it.
